flowchart LR
    U[Users<br/>AI Engineers / Analysts] --> W[Next.js Webapp<br/>App Router + React Query]
    W --> BFF[Next.js API Proxy Layer<br/>webapp/app/api/*]
    BFF --> API[FastAPI Retrieval API<br/>src/retrieval/api.py]

    API --> ING[Ingestion Catalog<br/>dataset/.ingestion/ingestion_catalog.json]
    API --> MILVUS[(Milvus Vector DB)]
    API --> OPENAI[OpenAI APIs<br/>Embeddings + LLM]
    API --> PROMPTS[Prompt Templates<br/>prompts/*]

    DS[(Workspace Data<br/>dataset/*)] --> PIPE[Ingestion Pipeline<br/>src/ingestion/*]
    PIPE --> ING

    ING --> IDX[Indexer<br/>src/retrieval/indexer.py]
    IDX --> MILVUS
    IDX --> OPENAI

    DOCS[(Platform Docs<br/>platform_documents/*.docx)] --> DOCING[Doc Ingestion<br/>chatbot/doc_ingestion.py]
    DOCING --> MILVUS
    DOCING --> OPENAI

    SUM[Artifact Summary Indexer] --> MILVUS
    SUM --> OPENAI
    PROF[Profile Indexer from Summaries] --> MILVUS
    PROF --> OPENAI

    AIR[Airflow DAG<br/>airflow/dags/ingestion_dag.py] --> PIPE
